JetBrains dotTrace 1.1.2 Maintenance Release

Posted by davidhayden on April 12, 2006

Looks like JetBrains just released a 1.1.2 maintenance release for dotTrace.  It has a few bug fixes and cosmetic changes as well as a new feature that looks interesting:



  • Integration with ReSharper unit test runner for ReSharper 2.0-beta and higher.

The release of ReSharper 2.0 has to be getting close now.


If you haven’t played with dotTrace yet, I wrote a simple walkthrough of dotTrace, JetBrains dotTrace – Profiling my Simple Winform Database Explorer and Code Generator, and JetBrains has a demo on their website.
